title: Violence erupts in Tel Aviv as Eritrean protesters clash with police
description: Violence erupted in Tel Aviv, Israel, as Eritrean protesters clashed with police. The Israeli prime minister said he wants all Eritrean migrants involved in the violent clash to be deported.

title: Eritrean migrants involved in violent clashes should be deported, Israel’s Netanyahu says
description: After violent clashes between Eritrean migrants in Tel Aviv, Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu said Sunday he wants those involved to be deported.

title: Tens of thousands have signed up for contract military service this year, former Russian president says
description: Tens of thousands of people have signed up for professional service with the Russian military since the start of the year, state media quoted the country's former president as saying Sunday.

title: Inside Putin's push to rewrite Russian history in favor of his war in Ukraine
description: Russian high school seniors will return to classrooms this week to find history rewritten in the image of President Vladimir Putin.

title: North Korea stages 'tactical nuclear attack' drill with mock warhead
description: North Korea conducted a simulated “tactical nuclear attack” drill on Saturday that included two long-range cruise missiles, state media reported on Sunday.
